Cats in R console.

Source: R/kittyR.R
kittyR.Rd

Cats in R console.

kittyR(meow = TRUE, sound = 3)

Arguments

meow

Logical that decides whether to play a meow sound along with the picture of a cat.
sound

A character string or a number specifying what sound to be played by either specifying one of the built in sounds, specifying the path to a .wav file or specifying an url. There are currently 6 meows included. The default is 1.

Value

A photo of a cat is downloaded and displayed in the plot window.

Examples

kittyR::kittyR(meow = FALSE)
